        "content": "<div><p>Hooray!  We dreamed this 10 years ago when trying to advertise campus-wide events during the year of Art and Nature&#8230; where are they?  We&#8217;ve put up some images from the Arthur Loeb Design Science Collection, which we invite any and all to come and explore in Carr Haus 001.\n</p><p/></div>", 
