        "content": "<div><p>&gt; Will this acronym have a function?</p>\n<p>In answer to Miguel&#8217;s question, it appears it&#8217;s having a great function right now on this interesting strand. When everyone talks about &#8220;lead&#8221; I think Pb (chemical symbol for Lead) which makes me think of Pbj (Peanut Butter Jelly). Which reminds me of my <a href=\"http://two.risd.edu/2008/09/04/what-makes-risd/#comment-1166\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peanut Butter and Jelly Challenge</a>. -JM\n</p><p/></div>", 
