        "content": "<div><p>And congratulations to <strong>Katrina Vonnegut &#8216;09 FD</strong>, whose <a href=\"http://our.risd.edu/2008/11/20/cradle-of-victory/\" rel=\"nofollow\">&#8220;Cradle Chair&#8221; has won first place</a> in the Billes Products International Design Contest [New Orleans] for new designs in furnishings and accessories.\n</p><p/></div>", 
