        "content": "<div><p>Cooperstown Art Association announces its 2009 National Exhibition.</p>\n<p>Details, such as eligibility, requirements, deadlines, exhibition dates and prize amounts can be found on their site:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.cooperstownart.com/national.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.cooperstownart.com/national.html</a>\n</p><p/></div>", 
