        "content": "<div><p>Thanks to everyone for stepping up to the challenging tasks of assuming new leadership roles on Staff Council, and thanks to outgoing Chair Candy Seel for shepherding tons of Staff Council activity for our RISD. Best wishes, JM\n</p><p/></div>", 
        "date": "Thu, 08 Jan 2009 23:22:00"
