        "content": "<div><p>The WW @ Work program works!!!  I&#8217;ve lost 42 pounds since I signed up last fall.  Really.  Come join us.  WW has never worked for me before but somehow going over to the Library once a week with other RISD folks is easy and fun.\n</p><p/></div>", 
