        "author": "Ariel Bordeaux", 
        "content": "<div><p>I&#8217;m happy to see some interest in bringing this film to risd. I&#8217;d love to help facilitate in any way possible.\n</p><p/></div>", 
        "date": "Mon, 20 Apr 2009 13:54:00"
