        "author": "Lincoln Bostian", 
        "content": "<div><p>Hello,<br/>\nI am pushing for increased exposure of RISD students to the Virtual Reality CAVE at Brown as well as more funding for advancements to Brown&#8217;s Virtual Reality program. The possibilities for RISD&#8217;s use of the CAVE are endless&#8211;everything from apparel design to installation art to architecture. In fact, every major could potentially benefit from exposure to the CAVE. I have resarched some immediate action ideas and am more than willing to discuss if people are interested. I am currently in the only RISD/Brown class which deals with scientific data visualization in virtual reality, and it really is a sight to behold!</p>\n<p>&#8211;Lincoln\n</p><p/></div>", 
