        "content": "<div><p>If appropriate, I&#8217;d also like to <a href=\"http://www.brown.edu/Project/Interrupt_2008/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">advertise this</a><br/>\nIt&#8217;s a digital media writing &amp; performance festival&#8211;now on up the hill.  I&#8217;m hosting a fringe event at 10pm-midnight Saturday night, I suspect it&#8217;ll be low-tech or no-tech.  It&#8217;s programmed by the festibal organizers (John Cayley + Justin Katko) but I think I&#8217;ll have slots for RISD poets.  Please contact me if you&#8217;re interested <a href=\"mailto:mbyrne@risd.edu\">mbyrne@risd.edu</a>\n</p><p/></div>", 
