        "author": "Gail Geisser", 
        "content": "<div><p>To all faculty, staff and students.<br/>\nYou can now place interlibrary loan requests online.  Just go to the RISD Library intranet site and click on which interlibrary loan form you need under HTML content.  Once you submit your request, it will be sent to <a href=\"mailto:risdlib@risd.edu\">risdlib@risd.edu</a> where I will receive it.  If you have any questions, please call or email me.<br/>\nThanks,<br/>\nGail\n</p><p/></div>", 
