        "content": "<div><p>Hi Gail&#8211;<br/>\nI started a new thread on this. I also want to remind everyone about <a href=\"http://two.risd.edu/2008/10/10/college-hill-libraries-unite/\" rel=\"nofollow\">this other exciting library news</a> already posted on two.risd!<br/>\nThanks,<br/>\nLiz\n</p><p/></div>", 
