        "content": "<div><p>Digital Display and the new school calendar</p>\n<p>I am wondering how do people feel about them, after half a semester.<br/>\nI tried to promote events on it, and I feel that it is less efficient than traditional posters.<br/>\nI also understood that we had our first incident of inappropriate material published onto the display.</p>\n<p>Are there anything that are in the works to improve the system? Does anyone have any suggestions to improve it?\n</p><p/></div>", 
