        "author": "Elizabeth Leuthner", 
        "content": "<div><p>Hi Tino&#8211;<br/>\nDo you think this discussion might take place on the existing thread &#8220;<a href=\"http://two.risd.edu/2008/08/26/digital-bulletin-boards/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Digital Bulletin Boards</a>&#8221; (begun August 26) or do you feel it warrants a new thread entirely? I&#8217;m just trying to keep related discussions together, wherever possible (and appropriate). Happy to do either, however.<br/>\nBest from,<br/>\nLiz\n</p><p/></div>", 
