        "content": "<div><p>I&#8217;d like to get a communal response to the idea that &#8220;Printing Should Be Free.&#8221; What are your opinions and experiences with the printing protocol at RISD- it&#8217;s financial burden, technical efficiency and working constraints on your generative process? I&#8217;d especially like input from graphic design students or other majors who rely heavily on printing for their production and work flow.\n</p><p/></div>", 
