        "author": "Elizabeth Leuthner", 
        "content": "<div><p>Hi Lynn&#8211;<br/>\nI started a new discussion on your topic of free printing <a href=\"http://two.risd.edu/2008/11/21/freedom-of-print/\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>. I feel certain this topic was broached earlier on two.risd, but cannot for the life of me find the thread right now. I will continue to look, as it might provide some context (or not?!).<br/>\nBest from,<br/>\nLiz\n</p><p/></div>", 
