        "author": "Claudia Covert", 
        "content": "<div><p>The first floor of the Library will be open until midnight the following days:<br/>\nMonday, Dec 1<br/>\nTuesday, Dec 2<br/>\nWednesday, Dec 3<br/>\nThursday, Dec 4<br/>\nSunday, Dec 7<br/>\nWe would appreciate knowing if these hours are useful.\n</p><p/></div>", 
