        "content": "<div><p>Hi. Not sure where to put this: would it be possible to somehow have not only our names but also departments or titles or some i.d. to accompany our postings? its nice sometimes to know if a conversation thats going on is with staff/faculty/students&#8230;and it is often difficult to tell.  just wondering&#8230; lucy/prof/gd.\n</p><p/></div>", 
