        "author": "Mairead Byrne", 
        "content": "<div><p>I actually like the first name, no rank democracy of the word kind of writing we have here.  I think there is a way though, to access threads according to group, e.g., students, staff, faculty.  That said, however, I actually would be very interested in what one specific group, i.e., alums, have to say, particularly about how the assignment-driven, almost macho culture here prepares them for life immediately after graduation, and for the workplace which, given our focus on art &amp; design, I&#8217;m sure they often have to invent.\n</p><p/></div>", 
