        "content": "<div><p>I am putting together a book for prospective art students and would like to give them advice from RISD students, alumni and faculty on building their portfolios and fulfilling their art school goals. Any tips or lessons you have learned along the way, interesting stories or even references/resources you used to get yourselves here would be great!</p>\n<p>I am also looking for sample portfolio works and essays used which were accepted to RISD and other art colleges.</p>\n<p>Please send any information/files along with your name, department and year of graduation to: <a href=\"mailto:jvizzacc@g.risd.edu\">jvizzacc@g.risd.edu</a></p>\n<p>Thanks!\n</p><p/></div>", 
