        "author": "Stephanie Grey", 
        "content": "<div><p>Hello! Hello!</p>\n<p>I teach part-time in the Graphic Design department and recently assigned my students a project centered around Bonniedale Farm in North Scituate, RI. I&#8217;m writing to inquire if there are others who may be involved in this effort, or if others would like to be.</p>\n<p>There was a recent article in the Providence Journal about the farm, which is home to many wonderful animals that would otherwise be homeless or destroyed. The farm will be closed in less than one month due to foreclosure.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s the Journal link if you&#8217;d like to read more:<br/><a href=\"http://www.projo.com/news/bobkerr/kerr_column_22_03-22-09_V3DOI72_v20.3260147.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.projo.com/news/bobkerr/kerr_column_22_03-22-09_V3DOI72_v20.3260147.html</a></p>\n<p>And here&#8217;s a link to my blog with a few more details:<br/><a href=\"http://stircenter.com/2009/04/08/413/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://stircenter.com/2009/04/08/413/</a></p>\n<p>Please contact me if you have an interest in this.<br/><a href=\"mailto:stephgrey@mac.com\">stephgrey@mac.com</a></p>\n<p>thank you!<br/>\nStephanie Grey\n</p><p/></div>", 
