        "author": "Selma-Rachel Swire", 
        "content": "<div><p>Hello Liz and the RISD Community,</p>\n<p>I am very interested in how students, faculty, and staff here at RISD feel about sustainability and environmental issues on the RISD campus. I would like to start a thread about RISD and our environmental impact.</p>\n<p>While researching this topic, I have discovered that many colleges and universities are banding together, pledging to address global warming and create climate neutral campuses. With the current economic environment, these actions on our campus might help us save our school&#8217;s money and decrease our carbon footprint as an institution</p>\n<p>See <a href=\"http://www.presidentsclimatecommitment.org/html/about.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.presidentsclimatecommitment.org/html/about.php</a> to learn more about this issue. </p>\n<p>Thanks!<br/>\n-Selma-Rachel Swire\n</p><p/></div>", 
        "date": "Sun, 12 Apr 2009 14:17:00"
